(32, 'openmic-w92-elainefaye-too-high', 92, 4, '{"week":"92","position":"4","slug":"openmic-w92-elainefaye-too-high","youtube":"Ww_wm-Vys6Q","steemuser":"elainefaye","permlink":"xne2on2f","title":"Too High","bgimage":"\\/assets\\/backgrounds\\/actor-adult-art-802195.jpg","link":"https:\\/\\/steemit.com\\/openmic\\/@elainefaye\\/xne2on2f","original":true,"has_lyrics":true,"lyrics":"I remember 24\\/7 I was by your side\\nsince the very night you came up to me and you told me\\nThat you like my style\\nIt was more than that, the way you look at me so deep gave me a heart attack\\nMusic Soulchild spinning in the back\\nYou took my hand we sang along and I knew for a fact that\\nI could lose my soul, though I\\u2019d give it all\\nRip out my heart as an offering and let it bleed\\n\\nTo you to you to you to you\\nYou know this all has been\\nFor you though we been going through\\nThese dark places that lovers\\nDo they do I know they do\\nBut I\\u2019ve been feelin\\u2019 so low\\nAfraid of losing our love\\nAnd in the dark of my mind I get lost\\nMaybe we were too high\\n\\nToo high off the lovin\\u2019\\nToo high off the smokin\\u2019\\nToo far gone to see through true eyes\\nWhen the smoke begin\\u2019s to settle\\nThe light begins to tremble\\nwill you recall the story of us\\n\\nMaybe we were to high...\\nMaybe we were to high...\\n\\nDo you remember me talking in my sleep\\nI\'d be so far gone\\nThe way you lay it down you put me out without a doubt\\nYour hands on my body\\nFelt just like a dream\\nEverything I ever wanted and could ever need\\nAnd now we barely speak\\nSo far gone though you\\u2019re right there next to me\\nEmotion killing me and I over think\\nGoin\\u2019 crazy search your phone analyzing everything\\n\\nYou do, you do, you do, you do\\nJust trying to find a way to break through\\nThe darkness in the room\\nI know that we been going through\\nThings its true that lovers do\\nBut I\\u2019ve been feelin\\u2019 so low\\nAfraid of losing our love\\nAnd in the dark of my mind I get lost\\nMaybe we were too high\\n\\nToo high off the lovin\\u2019\\nToo high off the smokin\\u2019\\nToo far gone to see through true eyes\\nWhen the smoke begin\\u2019s to settle\\nThe light begins to tremble\\nwill you recall the story of us\\n\\nMaybe we were to high...\\nMaybe we were to high...\\n\\nHow many time have I sought, this perfect picture of us\\nFutility, reality starts bleeding through\\nJust want a moment for us, to remember our love\\nOr is a memory the only thing that we cling to...","color":"#71695e"}'),
(33, 'openmic-w92-joseacabrerav-necesaria', 92, 5, '{"week":"92","position":"5","slug":"openmic-w92-joseacabrerav-necesaria","youtube":"MYqepQ36WR8","steemuser":"joseacabrerav","permlink":"steemit-openmic-semana-92-necesaria-original","title":"Necesaria","bgimage":"\\/assets\\/backgrounds\\/bloom-blossom-flora-130154.jpg","link":"https:\\/\\/steemit.com\\/openmic\\/@joseacabrerav\\/steemit-openmic-semana-92-necesaria-original","has_lyrics":true,"original":true,"lyrics":"Hace tiempo que buscaba\\nuna piel donde tatuarme,\\nuna calle pa pasearla agarrado de las cuerdas.\\nhace tiempo que perdia, ayer, para ser exactos.\\nEl tiempo en mil tonter\\u00edas,\\npor andar muy \\"Ocupado\\".\\nLa mision: una guerra de miradas,\\ngana el que menos aguante,\\nel que pierda los estribos\\nser\\u00e1 el que menos se tape.\\nDices cosas que no pueden salir mal.\\nMientes tanto que no veo la verdad.\\nHaces da\\u00f1o, ya no puedo respirar.\\nPero eres necesaria para andar.\\n\\nHace tiempo que te veo\\nPaseando por las aceras\\nY saltar de la ventana es de cuerdos,\\npor ti.\\n\\nDigo cosas que no pueden salir mal.\\nMiento poco, lo que tenga que ocultar.\\nHago da\\u00f1o, no te lo voy a negar,\\npero tengo lo que buscas, y algo m\\u00e1s.\\n\\nMi mision es perder en tu batalla pero ganarte la guerra.\\nObsequiarte mi pasado para que veas quien era,\\nsi te sientes asustada, espera a verme ahora.\\nYa no soy ni mi sombra.\\n\\nDices cosas que no pueden salir mal.\\nMientes tanto que no veo la verdad.\\nHaces da\\u00f1o, ya no puedo respirar.\\nPero eres necesaria para andar.\\n\\nDigo cosas que no pueden salir mal.\\nMiento poco, lo que tenga que ocultar.\\nHago da\\u00f1o, no te lo voy a negar,\\npero tengo lo que buscas, y algo m\\u00e1s.","color":"rgb(122,150,163)"}'),
(34, 'openmic-w91-samidbarid-remember-old-places', 91, 1, '{"week":"91","position":"1","slug":"openmic-w91-samidbarid-remember-old-places","youtube":"Y6-mk1Oo0ug","steemuser":"samidbarid","permlink":"steemit-openmic-week-91-sami-d-barid-feat-shavon-bonnie-legion-remember-old-places","title":"Remember old places","bgimage":"\\/assets\\/backgrounds\\/audio-mixer-buttons-close-up-159206.jpg","link":"https:\\/\\/steemit.com\\/openmic\\/@samidbarid\\/steemit-openmic-week-91-sami-d-barid-feat-shavon-bonnie-legion-remember-old-places","original":true,"color":"#ca9862"}'),
(35, 'openmic-w91-ilazramusic-mia', 91, 2, '{"week":"91","position":"2","slug":"openmic-w91-ilazramusic-mia","youtube":"iz9OB_K0J0Q","steemuser":"ilazramusic","permlink":"wxl0oo9x","title":"M\\u00eda","bgimage":"\\/assets\\/backgrounds\\/acoustic-art-band-327558.jpg","link":"https:\\/\\/steemit.com\\/openmic\\/@ilazramusic\\/wxl0oo9x","original":true,"has_lyrics":true,"lyrics":"Un, dos, tres, cuatro veces tuve que probarte,\\nPara darme cuenta y sentir que no estaba so\\u00f1ando,\\nY que el paladar estaba saboreando,\\nUna escultura totalmente definida como arte,\\nQuise mirarte mientras arrancabas esa blusa,\\nDe tu pecho de manera tan sutil pero,\\nNo pude mirar m\\u00e1s de dos segundos mi musa,\\nPues si miraba tres, te juro ya no iba a vivir,\\nSal\\u00ed con vida de esa habitaci\\u00f3n por suerte o magia,\\nCaminaste todo mi ser con la piel tan fr\\u00eda y descalza,\\nY mi calefacci\\u00f3n, era tu piel que en mi dorm\\u00eda, tus dedos a mi desvest\\u00edan,\\nY ya no quedaba m\\u00e1s nada, que una noche donde te ven\\u00edas,\\nAmor, y todo era una iron\\u00eda, pues mientras muchos te perd\\u00edan,\\nMi sue\\u00f1o se hacia realidad tan solo con llamarte...\\nSimplemente, m\\u00eda.","color":"#495b61"}'),
(36, 'openmic-w91-darrenclaxton-chapters-just-begun', 91, 3, '{"week":"91","position":"3","slug":"openmic-w91-darrenclaxton-chapters-just-begun","youtube":"_QCHb30xB-k","steemuser":"darrenclaxton","permlink":"ahzbtkml","title":"Chapters Just Begun","bgimage":"\\/assets\\/backgrounds\\/background-balance-beach-289586.jpg","link":"https:\\/\\/steemit.com\\/openmic\\/@darrenclaxton\\/ahzbtkml","has_lyrics":true,"original":true,"lyrics":"A long long time ago\\nmy boiling blood would flow\\nstraight into my head\\ncaused me oh such shame\\nand other peoples pain\\nconstant feelings strained\\n\\nI\'ve flaws that you can see\\nand others I can feel\\nbut most of them are gone\\nmost of all I\'m me\\nthe only one I\'ll be\\nrefreshing constantly\\n\\nTake me by the sea\\nlet me tell you stories\\nof how I used to be\\nlead me down the road\\nstories left untold\\nand chapters just begun\\nchapters just begun\\n\\nyears and years rolled by\\nI sat and wondered why\\nwhere it all went wrong\\nthe patience that I found\\nhad pinned me to the ground\\nmy tempers almost gone\\n\\nTake me by the sea\\nlet me tell you stories\\nof how I used to be\\nlead me down the road\\nstories left untold\\nand chapters just begun\\nchapters just begun\\n\\nTake me by the sea\\nlet me tell you stories\\nof how I used to be\\ntake me down the road\\nof tales left untold\\nand chapters just begun\\nchapters just begun\\n\\nI\'ve flaws that you can see\\nand others I can feel\\nbut most of them are gone\\nmost of all I\'m me\\nthe only one I\'ll be\\nrefreshing constantly","color":"#8E7E71"}'),
